xkgzszOne.yzsql:
select  case when   exists(
select * from ( SELECT xn,
                                          xq,
                                          kcdm,
                                          xh,
                                          zzzscj,
                                          ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY kcdm, xh ORDER BY xn desc, xq desc, zzzscj desc) AS rn
                                     FROM t_cj_xscjb
                                    where kcdm = #{p_kcdm_cxrw_zckc} 
                                      and xh = #{xkxg_xsOne.xh}) where rn!=1 and zzzscj>=60) then 'XKGL.OPERATE.RESULT_XDCSYDSXBKXD' else '1' end from dual ;
 select distinct
    CASE 
        WHEN  (select   a.zzcj end from   (select jbyydm,xh,max(zzcj)zzcj from     T_KS_SLJKSCJB group by jbyydm,xh )   a where a.xh = #{xkxg_xsOne.xh} and a.jbyydm=b.jbyydm   ) >=b.KSCJYQ
            THEN '1'
        ELSE 'XKGL.OPERATE.RESULT_KCWYDJBFHBKXD'
    END AS result from t_rw_rwapb b where id= #{ p_rwid} and KSCJYQ is not null ;
 select case when #{p_rwid} is null then '1' else
   (  
  case when (select count(1) from t_rw_rwap_kxkxsmd    where rwid=#{p_rwid} ) > 0 then 
  nvl ((select distinct '1'  from t_rw_rwapb where xn=#{p_xn}and xq=#{p_xq} and kcdm = #{rwOne.kcdm} and 
 id in(
 select rwid from t_rw_rwap_kxkxsmd  where xh = #{p_xh})),'XKGL.OPERATE.RESULT_BFHKXMDBKXD' ) else '1' end ) end sxz   from dual

xkgzszOne.sfbsxsql:
select dm, sfbsx
          from (select 'SFKXDNJK' dm, '1' sfbsx
                  from dual
                union
                select 'SFKXGNJK' dm, '1' sfbsx
                  from dual
                union
                select 'SFKYX' dm, '1' sfbsx
                  from dual
                union
                select 'SFYXKXQ' dm, '1' sfbsx
                  from dual
                union
                select 'SFKZYFX' dm, '1' sfbsx
                  from dual
                union
                select 'sfkzy' dm, '1' sfbsx
                  from dual
                union
                select 'sfkbj' dm, '1' sfbsx
                  from dual
                   union
               select 'sfkzsjct' dm, case when ( select count(*) from (select *  from  t_zy_xssjzyb a where a.xkfsdm in('sxw-b-b','bx-b-b')
 and a.xn=#{p_xn} and a.xq=#{p_xq} and a.xh= #{p_xh}) a  
, (select * from t_pk_pkjgb where rwid = #{p_rwid} )b where f_pk_sjctjs(a.zc,b.zc)>0 and a.xqj=b.xqj and  not (a.ksjc > b.jsjc or a.jsjc<b.ksjc)
 )>0 then '1' else '0' end sfbsx  from dual 
) where ( #{p_kcdm_cxrw_zckc}   in(select kcdm from t_rw_rwapb where xn=#{p_xn} and xq=#{p_xq} and rwlx='xmjxrw')) or   (  not exists (select  a.xn,a.xq   from t_rw_dgbjb a left join t_rw_rwapb b on a.rwid=b.id where b.kcdm = #{p_kcdm_cxrw_zckc}
                      and a.bjdm= #{xkxg_xsOne.bjdm} and a.xn=#{p_xn} and a.xq=#{p_xq} ))
  or  ( select count(*) from (select *  from  t_zy_xssjzyb a where a.xkfsdm  in('sxw-b-b','bx-b-b')
 and a.xn=#{p_xn} and a.xq=#{p_xq} and a.xh= #{p_xh}) a  
, (select * from t_pk_pkjgb where rwid = #{p_rwid} )b where f_pk_sjctjs(a.zc,b.zc)>0 and a.xqj=b.xqj and  not (a.ksjc > b.jsjc or a.jsjc<b.ksjc)
 )>0
